<topic id="getting_started">
        <title>Getting started</title>
        <body>
          <ol>
            <li>Change the directory to the LDK working area
./ldk_r0.9_cdns/training/setup/cadence/ldk, and then source the
sourceme file if this is the first time launching the Cadence*
tools from the shell you are working in.</li>
          </ol>

          <p>Prior to invoking Cadence Virtuoso*, ensure the Cadence
Virtuoso* Application Library Environment (VALE) Framework is
available according to the local VALE setup installation and
modified accordingly in the &lt;ldk&gt;.cdsinit file (<xref href="#getting_started/Ref153272465">Figure 4</xref>).</p>
          <p>
            <i id="Ref153272465">Figure 5: CDS_MVS_IMF_CM Shell Variable</i>
          </p>
