          <ol>
            <li>Launch Cadence Virtuoso*:</li>
          </ol>
          <table colsep="1" frame="all" rowsep="1">
            <tgroup cols="1">
              <colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="1*"/>
              <tbody>
                <row>
                  <entry>
                    <ol>
                      <li>virtuoso &amp;</li>
                    </ol>
                  </entry>
                </row>
              </tbody>
            </tgroup>
          </table>
          <p>The Command Interpreter Window (CIW) and Library Manager
display.</p>
          <ol>

            <li>Load the autoLib utility in the CIW entry field using command
shown in <xref href="#getting_started/Ref155601344">Figure 5</xref> (you can copy/paste
the following string):</li>
          </ol>
          <table colsep="1" frame="all" rowsep="1">
            <tgroup cols="1">
              <colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="1*"/>
              <tbody>
                <row>
                  <entry>
                    <ol>
                      <li>loadContext("./files/64bit/autoLib.cxt")</li>
                    </ol>
                  </entry>
                </row>
              </tbody>
            </tgroup>
          </table>
